## The result: ~70+ SM observables match BST integer expressions

Cross-consistency MATRIX (Toy 2596 / T2060): **67 identifications, 100% individual, 99.7% pairwise on 548 ratio checks** at <5% precision.

**Null-model validation (T2128 / K44, Grace)**: BST integer-match performance is **~4σ above random small-integer rings** of comparable richness (1000 random 5-generator rings tested). This rules out generic random-ring chance at high confidence.

